aha_ott_http_probe: This job is used for HTTP probing to monitor the availability of your Aha OTT application (running on port 3000). It checks for HTTP 200 responses.

aha_ott_metrics: This job monitors the system-level metrics (CPU, memory, disk) using Node Exporter running on port 9100.

aha_ott_kubernetes: This job uses Kubernetes SD (Service Discovery) to automatically discover pods in your Kubernetes cluster and collect metrics from them.

Notes:
Replace IP with the actual IP address or DNS name where your Aha OTT service is running.

Modify the replacement value to match the correct exporter or monitoring instance's IP address (13.232.214.2:9115 is just an example).
